t <- function(x) {
  # check if x is numeric
  if(is.numeric(x)) {
    return (x)
  }
  l <- LabelEncoder.fit(x)
  y <- transform(l, x)
  return (y)
}

knn.test.X <- sapply(pd.test.X, t)

  # check if x is numeric
  if(is.numeric(x)) {
    return (x)
  }

  return (y)
}
